WEBVTT

00:01:28.958 --> 00:01:30.998
u 15:30, sklupčali bismo se

00:01:30.998 --> 00:01:34.258
pokraj TV-a

00:01:34.258 --> 00:01:36.734
i toliko stišali ton na TV-u

00:01:36.734 --> 00:01:39.527
da ga je bilo gotovo nemoguće čuti.

00:01:39.527 --> 00:01:41.838
Ponekad kad bismo to radili,

00:01:41.838 --> 00:01:44.270
toliko smo govorili "šššš", 
toliko je "šššš-ova"

00:01:44.270 --> 00:01:46.135
prolazilo kućom

00:01:46.135 --> 00:01:48.110
da sam nas zamišljao poput

00:01:48.110 --> 00:01:51.610
posade njemačke podmornice

00:01:51.610 --> 00:01:54.102
koja se šulja rubom oceana

00:01:54.102 --> 00:01:55.918
dok na površini

00:01:55.918 --> 00:01:59.663
patrolira HMS Podočnjak,

00:01:59.663 --> 00:02:01.790
spreman osuditi nas na smrt